                  </persName>
             sworn.</p>
               <p>I am a pawn-broker, the corner of Walker's-Court, Little Pultney-street; on the 30th of July, the prisoner Upton pledged this shirt with me for half-a-crown.</p>
               <p>(Deposed to by the prosecutor.)</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17870912-6-person111">
                  JOHN
                   BOYD
               <interp inst="t17870912-6-person111" type="surname" value="BOYD"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17870912-6-person111" type="given" value="JOHN"></interp>
